^B@2^*BMM: We regret we could not capture all the teaching part, particularly on the play of the hand, in this board as transcription is not one of our major attribute. However, a pass after a redirecting double shows 2-card support and a bid at the 2-level shows a 3-card support. But we received the following comments from Howard, how Board 5 was defended, while we were making this presentation.^*N|
