^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|This was a good board to bid grand slam. But first let me discuss an important comment on play - tricks six and seven. At tricks six and seven, on the @HK and @HQ declarer should throw 2 clubs, not a diamond and a club. Then there is no need to take the club finesse.|
